# Trigger: ship

If the user's message is **only** `ship` (case-insensitive, no other words), or they use the **`/ship`** slash command, execute the workflow in `.cursor/commands/ship.md` immediately: build, commit on `develop`, push, open or show PR to `main`.

Optional words after `ship` in chat (e.g. `ship fix pricing`) = commit message.
